data.description: Welcome to your Paradise Retreat.  If you want privacy this home has it.  2.7 Serene acres with beautiful landscaping.  Circular drive on secluded wooded lot.  Home has been updated with Newer Roof, Updated electric, New  High efficiency heat pump/AC, New plumbing, New Septic system (to be installed), New wall to wall carpet, New range.   This home has 3 Bedrooms and 1.5 Baths. Formal Living and Dining room,  Family room with floor to ceiling Brick Fa~ade for your wood stove. Attached 2 car garage and a detached 2 car garage/barn with a second floor loft.  Move in condition.  Only 4 miles to route 30 by pass.  Separate 1 acre lot tax ID# 0038.0100 is included with sale. Total acreage is 2.7 Owner is also willing to convert powder room to a full bath for minimal cost.
